This is a test to learn how to create a mcp server.

To use this, you need to use llama3.

You need to have an api key for accuweather and a .env file with the following variables:

ACCUWEATHER_API_KEY

You can get an api key for accuweather at https://developer.accuweather.com/ 

To run the server, you need to run the following command:

python main.py

